data.description: A phenomenal deal you wont want to miss out on! Two homes on just shy of 40 acres that have a combination of 9 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms and over 5000 square feet.  Embark on a journey of 40 acres of fully fenced mature pasture accented by cross fencing, with west facing views of glorious Colorado Sunsets. Enjoy the peace of mind of tranquil country living with the luxury of a short drive to the town of Calhan and highway 24. The property is a short commute to Falcon or Colorado Springs, so dump that city traffic and change out your rush hour frustration to calm commutes with country ease and fresh air. The main home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on the main level with an additional two bedrooms, a roughed in plumbed bath and an unfinished basement recreational area. This home has a pellet stove that keeps the home warm and cozy during those brisk Colorado Winters. All appliances are included with the home! Even the washer and dryer and garage freezers! The second home is a ranch style that has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms all on the main level, and even has its very own mailing address!- making this home perfect for a rental opportunity, home based business, or multi generational living. The property can also be legally subdivided, and this information can be found with the El Paso county assessors office. All kitchen appliances are included in this home also! Each home has their own septic and propane tanks with a shared well and trash, making the utilities incredibly affordable. The property also features a 30x40 steel barn perfect for your hobbies, livestock or homesteading dreams, or extra storage. The loafing shed is ready for your livestock or animals, so bring the entire family and settle down into this oasis of freedom, and enjoy all that Colorado Rural living has to offer!
